summary: even if those were jokes u can’t defend shane being racist and hanging out with racist people. he has done blackface, used the...
question: even if those were jokes u can’t defend shane being racist and hanging out with racist people. he has done blackface, used the n-word, and is bffs with jeffrey star like... he isn’t a good person regardless 🤔
answer:
Personally, I believe he’s changed a LOT since he did blackface and I haven’t personally even heard him say the n word and like I know I’m white so I’m not really in a position to forgive him but… he’s changed a lot. And idk about Jeffery I just dgaf about him honestly. Also, I’m not defending those past actions. At all.

But this is about Shane being a paedophile and humping his cat which is COMPLETELY different. Just because you think he’s racist it doesn’t mean you can just accuse him of shit he’s just made bad jokes about. That’s not how it works.

title: CHIANG MAI Digital Nomads Capital
body:
